{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Am I Nima?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You don't remember who you are. Act like her. Talk like her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Am I Nima</strong> puts you in control of Nima's brain. Explore rooms, unlock hidden memories, and piece together what really happened to Nima.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Start with a blank slate and discover new words and concepts as you explore and combine words together. Learn more about Nima by examining her room and possessions and use that knowledge to pass the series of tests your mother puts you through. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why has she trapped you in the basement? Why is she putting you through these tests? And why can't you stop the pain in your head?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Demo Edition includes Chapter 1 of the full game!\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combine</strong> words and concepts to answer the questions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong> your bedroom to discover who you were</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join us on <strong>Discord</strong> to help influence the game and see sneak pics of the future chapters!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736464719","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317110/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736464719","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317110/0990c3ab7da27f79d9bcc8f50019290e50018a37/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736464719","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317110/0990c3ab7da27f79d9bcc8f50019290e50018a37/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736464719","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content